body:
Comment 5: 
A bit more data, all tests done with the string "test a reasonable sized string that can
be compressed": 

- python can inflate zlib-deflated string
- zlib can inflate python-deflated string
- neither zlib nor python can inflate go-deflated string
- go can not inflate either of the compressed strings. 

The tokens passed to writeBlock from Go contain only literals (no offsets).
